tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE algorithmic_trading_strategies (
    strategy_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    strategy_name VARCHAR(255),
    market_data_volume DECIMAL(10,2),
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE Orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol VARCHAR(10),
  order_type VARCHAR(10),
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  order_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE TradeHistory (
  trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol VARCHAR(10),
  quantity INT,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  trade_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE MarketData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol VARCHAR(50),
  price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  volume INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol VARCHAR(50),
  price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  order_type VARCHAR(10),
  quantity INT,
  status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE market_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    price DECIMAL,
    volume INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_id INT,
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    buy_price DECIMAL,
    sell_price DECIMAL,
    profit DECIMAL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE strategy_performance (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    strategy_id INT,
    success_rate FLOAT,
    total_trades INT,
    cumulative_profit DECIMAL,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trade_alerts (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    alert_id INT,
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    alert_type VARCHAR(20),
    description TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
